	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />No, it's not for a video. It's actually about playing the game.<br /><br />I was thinking about a story mode similar to the one for the new &quot;Mortal Kombat&quot; game. Of course, &quot;Street Fighter II&quot; wouldn't include those cinematic cut scenes. But if determining the opponents' order had been easy, my next question would have been about including scenes like the ones in the end:<br /><br /><img src="http://i62.tinypic.com/outji8.png" alt="Image" /><br /><br />I think it would be interesting to be able to include those scenes before the battles. So you could have the fighters exchange some dialog before they start fighting.<br /><br />Combine all this and you can do an actual story mode with a realistic tournament schedule.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
